cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CY

This paper deals with sentiment analysis using Machine Learning and Natural Language Processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses Deep Learning algorithms, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. The paper deals with text data, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another possible sub-category. The use of Machine Learning and Natural Language Processing techniques also falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with digital text analytics, which makes cs.CY (Computers and Society) another possible sub-category.
